{"tid":841045,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"★中華廠商會會長：要求將「勞工假」與「銀行假」統一至12日！","createTime":"2018-09-29T09:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T08:48:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"528592525473b45091236f13512707ec538bbb8a","tid":841045,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】藍領打工仔每年只有12日法定勞工假假期，與白領享受的公眾假期少達5日之多，勞工團體一直要求盡快將「勞工假」與「銀行假」統一至17日。<br />\n<br />\n作為資方代表的中華廠商聯合會會長吳宏斌，今日表明贊成「統一」假期，認為「銀行假」應要向「勞工假」看齊，由放17日減至放12日。<br />\n<br />\n吳宏斌出席電台節目時批評白領放假太多。他解釋，推行5天工作周後，大部分白領已由每周工作6天減為5天，又有十幾天大假，又有17天公眾假期，「一年365日，返得240幾日，即係兩日休一日，返工三分二時間，有三分一在開心緊」。<br />\n<br />\n他因而贊成將白領的公眾假期，<span style=\"color: red;\">與藍領的勞工假看齊，即白領都只放12天假期，這便能一視同仁。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%9B%E5%81%875%E5%A4%A9-%E8%B4%8A%E6%88%90%E7%B5%B1-%E7%99%BD%E9%A0%98%E8%97%8D%E9%A0%98%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F-%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C%E5%90%B3%E5%AE%8F%E6%96%8C-%E9%BD%8A%E6%94%BE12%E6%97%A5-064400678.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2581%25875%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E8%25B4%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B5%25B1-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%259C%259F-%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%25AE%258F%25E6%2596%258C-%25E9%25BD%258A%25E6%2594%25BE12%25E6%2597%25A5-064400678.html&d=Rk%2FbIM7tdILA6ESJHrBbmOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=00160d8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%9B%E5%81%875%E5%A4%A9-%E8%B4%8A%E6%88%90%E7%B5%B1-%E7%99%BD%E9%A0%98%E8%97%8D%E9%A0%98%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F-%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C%E5%90%B3%E5%AE%8F%E6%96%8C-%E9%BD%8A%E6%94%BE12%E6%97%A5-064400678.html</a>"},{"pid":"f2ea657f43ffa2fdcc9844b4337eb97d66cf9187","tid":841045,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/h5EEGT9m4NPOmZA9fLDgqQ--%7EA/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c